short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Create, Save and Revisit versions of your Fantasy Team before the season starts, and have key insights into your team!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Introducing the Game Changer! This Chrome extension allows you to save and revisit previous versions of your AFL Fantasy team, making it easier to track changes and strategies over time. With just a click, you can save your current team lineup and compare it to previous versions, helping you make informed decisions about future trades. You also get access to state of the art tools and stats to help inform you make trades! Whether you're a seasoned AFL Fantasy player or just starting out, this extension is a must-have tool for optimizing your team performance and staying ahead of the competition.
